<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none;padding:0"><div class="NavHead" style="font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left">Legislation</div><div class="NavContent hlist" style="font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center">
