<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electronic_Communications_Privacy_Act" title="Electronic Communications Privacy Act">ECPA</a></li>
<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patriot_Act" title="Patriot Act">Patriot Act</a></li>
<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Homeland_Security_Act" title="Homeland Security Act">Homeland Security Act</a></li>
<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Protect_America_Act_of_2007" title="Protect America Act of 2007">Protect America Act of 2007</a></li>
<li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Foreign_Intelligence_Surveillance_Act_of_1978_Amendments_Act_of_2008" title="Foreign Intelligence Surveillance Act of 1978 Amendments Act of 2008">FISA Amendments Act of 2008</a></li></ul></div></div></td>
</tr><tr><td style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em">
